'''Green3''' was a [[Datafile/Legends|datafile]] that [[Green Squad]] had to capture in a training exercise in [[Alliance Training Center-5/Green Squad]] before they could become [[Green Squad 3]]. The file was stored aboard a simulated [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]]. When the group retrieved the file, the training exercise did not end like it was meant to; instead, an alarm came on, as the base was under attack from the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

